He points out that while there were no dismissals on Staten Island and there were few dismissals in Upper East Side or Tribeca schools, 17 school support staff lost seats in district 23 in Brownsville, Brooklyn, and 46 had to leave for Districts 8 and 9 in the South Bronx.
