Disappointing?
"No," stresses Eric Blanche, CEO of Adapt, an organization that organizes a week of employment for the disabled."
"In 15 years, significant progress has been made".
"At the time, the unemployment rate was not 2 but 3 times higher".
"But there's still a lot of work to be done."
